casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Jonathan David HEWITT-EL, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 155239
COA: 332946 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 16, 2018

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of defendant-appellant to file a supplemental brief after remand is GRANTED. The supplemental brief submitted on May 14, 2018, is accepted for filing.
